_sText: Gg_stoo_chinzak_devtex ---------------------------- *** IMPORTANT NOTE *** I'VE RELEASED A SECOND, IMPROVED VERSION OF THIS MAP. YOU CAN FIND IT HERE: GG_STOO_CZKTWO. I'M KEEPING THIS VERSION AROUND FOR POSTERITY, AND IN CASE ANYONE PREFERS IT TO THE NEW ONE. This took a few days to do, on and off. Almost everything in the map has been altered in some way. The other Chinzak for GG is barely altered from the original DM map. People would leave the server when it came on, saying it was too laggy or too hard to navigate. This map is a response to those complaints. Should be considerably easier to navigate than the original DM map. Should also run considerably faster despite having high-res cubemaps and high-res lightmaps. This is the first release so there may be problems I haven't found on my own. If so, I'll release a fixed version. Features a few custom textures created by me. Learning Photoshop as I go. Compile time on my very average PC was 5 mins exactly. VBSP took about 2 seconds. VVIS took about 5 seconds. VRAD took about 4 mins 53 seconds. :) Hope you enjoy playing this map as much as I enjoyed making it. Cheers to _TIF_ who made the original DM map in the first place! StOo (www.betaneutral.com)
